    • Constructor Detail

      • MockerJavaSourceFile

        public MockerJavaSourceFile(java.lang.String mockedName,
                    java.lang.String code)
        Constructs a mocker source code file to mock the class named mockedName with the class defined in code. Make sure that the package and class name stated in the source code match the ones in mockedName!
        Parameters:
        mockedName - The name of the class to be mocked.
        code - The source code to mock the class with.
